<ref>[http://tw.money.yahoo.com/news_article/adbf/d_a_080910_1_14ry3 〈系統晶片國家型計畫成果展 凌陽推內嵌處理器〉，中央社，2009/9/10]</ref>，為台灣第一顆自主架構設計並成功商品化之32-bit內嵌式處理器<ref>[http://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news_content/url/d/a/080910/3/14rs7.html 〈凌陽展出32位元內嵌式處理器核心技術〉，時報資訊，2009/9/10]{{dead link|date=2018年3月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://findingheros.blogspot.com/2008/10/32.html |title=〈凌陽首創32位元內嵌式處理器核心〉，Compotech Asia雜誌，2008-10月號 |accessdate=2009-04-02 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305010043/http://findingheros.blogspot.com/2008/10/32.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sunplus.com/chinese/press/press.asp?id=423B29493A2C268 |title=〈凌陽科技32位元內嵌式處理器　榮獲經濟部「卓越產業貢獻獎」〉，凌陽科技，2006/9/25 |accessdate=2009-04-02 |archive-date=2008-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081228105521/http://www.sunplus.com/chinese/press/press.asp?id=423B29493A2C268 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sunplus.com/chinese/press/press.asp?id=30291837281A242 |title=〈凌陽科技32位元處理器S<sup>+</sup>Core®獲頒「最佳創新獎」〉，凌陽科技，2006/5/23 |accessdate=2009-04-02 |archive-date=2008-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081228105512/http://www.sunplus.com/chinese/press/press.asp?id=30291837281A242 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sunplus.com/chinese/press/press.asp?id=7174C4C3823240 |title=〈凌陽展出國人首顆自主架構32位元處理器核心S<sup>+</sup>core®平台 展現台灣系統單晶片技術生根茁壯的成果〉，凌陽科技，2006/5/1 |accessdate=2009-04-02 |archive-date=2006-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061118102649/http://www.sunplus.com/chinese/press/press.asp?id=7174C4C3823240 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sunplus.com/chinese/press/press.asp?id=953D49273B3A3 |title=〈凌陽科技發表首顆國內自主架構32位元處理器核心S<sup>+</sup>core®〉，凌陽科技，2005/6/13 |accessdate=2009-04-02 |archive-date=2008-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081228105536/http://www.sunplus.com/chinese/press/press.asp?id=953D49273B3A3 |dead-url=yes }}</